    static class SpecificTesterClasses.QuadToBDToQuadTester
extends TesterClasses.UnaryQuadrupleFunctionTester
    A tester class to test the conversion from Quadruple to BigDecimal and back to Quadruple.
    Obtains the test data from DataProviders.q2bd2qConversionDataList() and performs new Quadruple(operand.bigDecimalValue()) as the tested operation.

      • findExpectedResult

        protected BigDecimal findExpectedResult(Quadruple op)
        Calculates a BigDecimal value equal to the expected result of the conversion from Quadruple to BigDecimal and back to Quadruple.
        The expected result is the exact value of the Quadruple parameter, expressed as a BigDecimal. In cases of NaN, Infinity, and -Infinity throws a NumberFormatException and further processing is performed by the parent class.
        Overrides:
        findExpectedResult in class TesterClasses.UnaryFunctionTester<Quadruple,Quadruple>
        Parameters:
        op - the value to be converted
        Returns:
        the expected result of the tested operation as a BigDecimal
